## Location

* HaNoi, Vietnam
* Full-time

## Salary Expectation

* up to 30M

## Requirements

* Minimum 2 years of experience in equivalent position; 
* Has leadership qualities, has experience in team management; 
* Good teamwork skills;  endure high pressure, don't mind working;  skills of persuasive communication, presentation, good efficiency; 
* Understand the implementation of user research activities; 
* Inquisitive, capable of self-study well, unable to un-learn what is known to access new knowledge; 
* As a person who focuses on details, good English is an advantage.






### Responsibilities

* Understand the company's product orientation, capabilities & strategy; 
* Implement activities to collect, synthesize user feedback, monitor & analyze the activities of competitor companies in the market; 
* Develop a strategy for the product; 
* Building monitoring and management of Product Vision & Product Roadmap; 
* Prepare & present product status reports to management; 
* Work with other departments in the company to bring products to ultimate success.


### You can bring

* Income: 20,000,000 - 30,000,000 / month; 
* Allowance 1,000,000 VND / month for lunch, gasoline, car; 
* Unlimited use of Monkey products; 
* Opportunities to exchange and learn with major partners (Facebook, Coccoc ...); 
* To work at a company that has won many prestigious awards such as the First Prize for the Global Initiative in the US by US President Barack Obama awarded;  First prize Vietnamese Talent;  Top 1 children's favourite apps on App Store and Google Play…;
* Get access to and experience the best and most famous educational materials and applications in the world; 
* To work directly with leading language experts and educational experts of the US and Vietnam; 
* To be able to work in a positive, open-minded, start-up environment, ready to listen and share from boss to colleagues; 
* Sponsored the costs of the courses to develop their own professional capacity; 
* Be considered for salary increase 2 times/year;
* Productivity bonus, project bonus, initiative bonus, acceleration bonus, hot bonus, the reward for thinking of new ways of reward;  On holidays, Tet, there are gifts and prizes; 
* Be equipped with work equipment or allowances for personal use; 
* The number of days off, public holidays, Tet, personal leave is up to 28 days/year; 
* Attractive maternity regime for men and women; 
* Enjoy the benefits of social insurance, health insurance, unemployment insurance and other benefits according to the company's regulations;
* Periodic health check and enjoy high-quality examination package at major hospitals; 
* Enjoy not only fun benefits: Teabreak every day, weekly party, monthly birthday, annual travel; 
* And many other attractive benefits policy will be discussed at the Interview.

